1. Read configuration
2. Initialize leap motion controller handlers/etc
3. Instantiate Parrot client object.
	a. Instantiate TCP object.
	b. Establish a connection to the python client.
	c. Initialize the python client using the configuration.
4. Wait for takeoff gesture.
	a. Send takeoff gesture to client.
	b. Wait for ready signal, else report any errors.
	c. On ready signal, switch to flight mode

While In Flight:
	send flight commands to client.
	receive response.
	if response is not good:
		report it
		send landing command and wait for response.
		If timed out:
			report it and exit